{
  "stem": "11174.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Here, and there, Polish soldiers around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Came Erev Rosh Hashanah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the eve of Rosh Hashanah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went in to the rabbi's house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some Jewish men then gave me where to sleep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Rosh Hashanah, we went in to daven.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Rosh Hashanah at the rabbi's house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, sure enough, there was hand-to-hand [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] fights between the Polish army and the German army in that little town.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were standing at the window and seeing this-- what is it called?-- hand-to-hand-- Combat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Combat, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, finally, middle of davening, there was the-- was a rabbi there, a very, very gray guy, short man and old man-- old man.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He must have been at least in his 70s.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, all of a sudden, the-- the little town went hand-- from hand to hand, three, four times who controlled it, between the Polish and the German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, all of a sudden, it got quiet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know who is-- who is going to be-- all of a sudden, a German soldier, we see him through the window, comes up the steps and knocks on the door, very-- [INAUDIBLE] I don't know if I could go through another fear like this, if the heart would-- would-- would survive.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When he knocked on that door we all thought we going to be dead.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somehow, before the war, we didn't believe that it could be so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somehow, there was a feeling that they will kill.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have any-- yes, we did hear already in other towns where they occupied and people ran, that they shot Jewish people here and there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were so-- I tell you, if I wouldn't have been a younger, 21 years old, and strong-- it's [? unbelievable. ?] To describe that fear is unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
